    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_evestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな！　今日は私とトリエルの歌を\n聴いてくれてありがとう！",
      "startTime": 10.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 13.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_evestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "会場が揺れるほど盛り上がってるな\nこれが、ミクとトリエルの力を掛け合わせた結果か……",
      "startTime": 17.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "この曲を通して……トリエルの三人が\n私にとってかけがえのない友達になったの",
      "startTime": 25.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はもっともっと、みんなと繋がりたい\nここにいるみんなの心が知りたい！",
      "startTime": 35.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな想いを込めて歌ったけど……\nみんなに、届いたかな？",
      "startTime": 41.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6666665999983,
          "startTime": 44.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（四人の出番が終わった後も、会場の熱気は）\n（なかなか冷めることがなかった）",
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ミク、お疲れ様",
      "startTime": 52.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "私、疲れないよ？",
      "startTime": 54.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それでも言わせてくれ。お疲れ様\n本当にいいライブだったよ",
      "startTime": 60.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ありがとう",
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、詞を全部作り直すと言われた時は驚いたよ\n間に合うのかハラハラしたな",
      "startTime": 69.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku007.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルのみんなが\n私の本当の気持ちに気付かせてくれたの",
      "startTime": 74.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku008.m4a",
      "text": "他の誰でもない、私自身の想いを……歌いたい\nみんなに届けたい、って",
      "startTime": 82.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku009.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞のコンセプトも、『私をお祝いする歌』から\n『私と一緒にお祝いする歌』になって……",
      "startTime": 89.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku010.m4a",
      "text": "時間はなかったけど、変えて良かったなって思ってるよ",
      "startTime": 93.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、本当にいい曲だった\n四人の歌声が胸に沁みたよ",
      "startTime": 101.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku011.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、そう言ってもらえて嬉しいな",
      "startTime": 103.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku012.m4a",
      "text": "ライブでね、四人で放つ音の線がお客さんと繋がって\n一つの大きな円になっていく感覚がして……凄かった",
      "startTime": 114.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、トリエルは真っ白に澄んだ光に包まれてて\n私もその中で気持ち良く歌うことが出来たの",
      "startTime": 124.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku014.m4a",
      "text": "楽しかった。本当に楽しかった\nでも……",
      "startTime": 133.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ミク……？　どうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 135.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。トリエルはこの後も\n何かするんだよね？",
      "startTime": 141.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　そうだな\nライブ後はいつも、三人で打ち上げをしてるよ",
      "startTime": 145.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku016.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、トリエルはこの後もいっぱいお話しするんだ\n楽しそうだなって思って",
      "startTime": 154.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（……そうだ。同じステージに立った仲なんだ）\n（住む次元が違うことなんて、問題じゃない）",
      "startTime": 161.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ミク。打ち上げ、参加してみないか？",
      "startTime": 164.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku017.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　でも、トリエルは三人で\n楽しみたいんじゃないの？",
      "startTime": 171.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5733.333333299981,
          "startTime": 177.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなはずないだろう？\n一緒にステージに立った仲なんだ。あ、もしもし",
      "startTime": 176.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……三人とも、大歓迎だそうだ",
      "startTime": 184.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku018.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほんとに？　ほんとに？　嬉しい……！\n{user}さん、ありがとう！",
      "startTime": 194.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――打ち上げの後",
      "startTime": 198.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku019.m4a",
      "text": "打ち上げって初めてだったけど\n楽しかった～……",
      "startTime": 204.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かった\n三人とも目がキラキラしてたな",
      "startTime": 208.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-mku020.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんがリクエストした曲を歌ったら\nまさかあんなことになるなんて……",
      "startTime": 214.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、鈴村さんが倒れた時は本気で焦ったよ\n幸せ過ぎて気絶するとは……",
      "startTime": 221.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
